Double Tap if you wish your cleaning cloths could do this!😍 Watch until the end - we hope this makes you smile. This is the reason why we all have so many cloths...they literally work like magic!😉✨
-
The #DontRushChallenge is a fun virtual way of bringing people together to make them feel good about themselves, even though we are all staying safe in our own homes with nowhere to go! I thought we could put our own cleaning and home spin on the challenge rather than passing a makeup brush between us🙊
-
I really hope you enjoy watching this as much as I loved making it🥰 I literally couldn’t stop smiling watching it over and over, it really cheered me up. It was such a pleasure to bring these wonderful accounts together and I think you will agree that they all look amazing both in their comfies and glammed up🔥
-
Thank you to all of the fantastic accounts who took part with me. It takes courage to do this so give them some love💕
